}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"やっぱりこの曲、すっごい楽しい〜！\nそれに、最初のころより\n息がぴったり合うようになってきたよね！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"ev61-ep1-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"練習の成果がばっちり出てるってことかな。\nそれにしても、みんなすっごく楽しそうだったよ。\n私が止めなかったら、まだまだ練習してたんじゃない？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev61-ep1-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"りみ","body":"確かにそうかも。\n楽しくって、時間があっという間だったよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev61-ep1-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"たえ","body":"私、この曲好きだな。\nなんか、自然と体が動いてくるんだよね。\nジョギングするのもすっごい楽しいよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev61-ep1-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId